Package: whoFetalStandards
Type: Package
Title: Calculate z-scores and centiles in the WHO Fetal Standards
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Simon", family = "Parker",
           email = "simon.parker1471@outlook.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-8214-4496"))
  )
Maintainer: Simon Parker <simon.parker1471@outlook.com>
Description: Implements the WHO Fetal standards to allow users to convert fetal
    biometry to centiles and z-scores. Utilises the Fetal standards published
    by Kiserud et al. (2017). PLoS Med 14:e1002220. These are described 
    online at <https://srhr.org/fetalgrowthcalculator/>.
